<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَاجِبَاتُ الْإِمَام<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>اِتِّخَاذُ الْمَلِكِ الْبِطَانَةَ وَأَهْلَ الْبِسَاط<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٩ص٧٧:</span> بَابُ بِطَانَةِ الإِمَامِ وَأَهْلِ مَشُورَتِهِ <span class="c1">" ,<span class="c5"> البِطَانَةُ:</span> الدُّخَلاَءُ "</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>